Example data in mvMOBSTER format.

Source: R/data.R
example_mvmobster.Rd

Example data in mvMOBSTER format.

data(example_mvmobster)

Format

A tibble that represents the cytobands for hg19 chromosome (chr, from, to, cytoband and region).

References

hg19

Examples

data(example_mvmobster)
